dc_description_s: Alternate title: Stadtplan von Brighton mit militaergeographischen Eintragungen. Grossblatt 12, Blattbereich 39. Relief shown by 25 meter contour intervals and spot elevations. Gauss-Krueger grid. Legend is in English and German. With a list of abbreviations. Source: Ordnance Survey 1:10,560; 1934, 1936, 1937. Major city access roads are color coded. Accompanied by booklet: "Militaergeographische Einzelangaben ueber England; Objektbilder zu den militaergeographischen Objektkarten 1:250 000 und 1:10 000 der Mappe 12 Suedost-England und London"; of photographs and drawings of important military objectives, bridges, factories, etc. (sites are located on map). (Booklet 12 is missing.)
dc_publisher_s: Berlin : Generalstab des Heeres, Abt. für Kriegskarten und Vermessungswesen, IV. Mil. Geo., 1941.
